Exception handling: Add support for x86-64 Windows

In nacl_globals.h: We declare the array size (NACL_THREAD_MAX) in the
header so that sizeof() works on these arrays.  Otherwise we would
have to assume NACL_THREAD_MAX is the array size in
debug_exception_handler.c, an assumption which could get out of sync.

